graph TD
    A[Input Text] --> B[AutoTokenizer]
    B -->|Input IDs, Attention Mask| C[BERT Encoder Block]
    
    subgraph Self-Attention Mechanism
    C --> D[Query Vector]
    C --> E[Key Vector]
    C --> F[Value Vector]
    D & E --> G[Attention Scores]
    G & F --> H[Context Matrix]
    end
    
    H --> I[AutoModel Classification Head]
    I --> J[Predicted Logits]
